  "texts": [
    "An interactive web application is developed using Streamlit library for the user to send a prompt and receive a response.",
    "A feedback form is also provided for the user in the chat application.",
    "ResultsFigure 3 shows the user interface of the chatbot, where the user can enter prompts and receive responses.",
    "Table 1 displays sample results of the Applied Computer Science (ACS) chatbot's prompts and responses.",
    "The chatbot's responses are descriptive and contextually relevant to the prompts."
  ]
